{"marker":1,"text":"languages, also in v. 11"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:5","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Now there were Jews staying in Jerusalem, devout people from every nation "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 28:19","book":"Mat","chapter":28,"verse":19,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 1:5","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":5,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 1:16","book":"Gal","chapter":1,"verse":16,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" under heaven. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 28:19","book":"Mat","chapter":28,"verse":19},{"label":"Rm 1:5","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":5},{"label":"Gl 1:16","book":"Gal","chapter":1,"verse":16}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:6","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"When this sound occurred, a crowd came together and was confused because each one heard them speaking in his own language. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:7","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"They were astounded and amazed, saying, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss add to one another"},{"kind":"text","text":" “Look, aren’t all these who are speaking Galileans? "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 1:11","book":"Act","chapter":1,"verse":11,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 2:12","book":"Act","chapter":2,"verse":12,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 1:11","book":"Act","chapter":1,"verse":11},{"label":"Ac 2:12","book":"Act","chapter":2,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss add to one another"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"How is it that each of us can hear them in our own native language? "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Parthians, Medes, Elamites; those who live in Mesopotamia, in Judea and Cappadocia, Pontus and Asia, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 14:9","book":"Gen","chapter":14,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Kg 17:6","book":"2Ki","chapter":17,"verse":6,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 14:9","book":"Gen","chapter":14,"verse":9},{"label":"2Kg 17:6","book":"2Ki","chapter":17,"verse":6}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Phrygia and Pamphylia, Egypt and the parts of Libya near Cyrene; visitors from Rome (both Jews and converts), "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 23:15","book":"Mat","chapter":23,"verse":15,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 13:13","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":13,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 15:38","book":"Act","chapter":15,"verse":38,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 16:6","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":6,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 16:21","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":21,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 18:23","book":"Act","chapter":18,"verse":23,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 23:15","book":"Mat","chapter":23,"verse":15},{"label":"Ac 13:13","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":13},{"label":"Ac 15:38","book":"Act","chapter":15,"verse":38},{"label":"Ac 16:6","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":6},{"label":"Ac 16:21","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":21},{"label":"Ac 18:23","book":"Act","chapter":18,"verse":23}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Cretans and Arabs —we hear them declaring the magnificent acts of God in our own tongues.” "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"They were all astounded and perplexed, saying to one another, “What does this mean?” "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But some sneered and said, “They’re drunk on new wine.” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 17:32","book":"Act","chapter":17,"verse":32,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 14:23","book":"1Co","chapter":14,"verse":23,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 17:32","book":"Act","chapter":17,"verse":32},{"label":"1Co 14:23","book":"1Co","chapter":14,"verse":23}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Peter stood up with the Eleven, raised his voice, and proclaimed to them, “Fellow Jews and all you residents of Jerusalem, let this be known to you, and pay attention to my words. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For these people are not drunk, as you suppose, since it’s only nine in the morning. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit it’s the third hour of the day"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit it’s the third hour of the day"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"On the contrary, this is what was spoken through the prophet Joel:"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And it will be in the last days, says God,"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I will even pour out my Spirit"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I will display wonders in the heaven above"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The sun will be turned to darkness"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Then everyone who calls"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Fellow Israelites, listen to these words: This Jesus of Nazareth was a man attested to you by God with miracles, wonders, and signs that God did among you through him, just as you yourselves know. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 3:2","book":"Jhn","chapter":3,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 4:48","book":"Jhn","chapter":4,"verse":48,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 10:38","book":"Act","chapter":10,"verse":38,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 2:4","book":"Heb","chapter":2,"verse":4,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jn 3:2","book":"Jhn","chapter":3,"verse":2},{"label":"Jn 4:48","book":"Jhn","chapter":4,"verse":48},{"label":"Ac 10:38","book":"Act","chapter":10,"verse":38},{"label":"Heb 2:4","book":"Heb","chapter":2,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Though he was delivered up according to God’s determined plan and foreknowledge, you used "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss read you have taken"},{"kind":"text","text":" lawless people to nail him to a cross and kill him. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 26:24","book":"Mat","chapter":26,"verse":24,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 22:22","book":"Luk","chapter":22,"verse":22,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 24:20","book":"Luk","chapter":24,"verse":20,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 3:18","book":"Act","chapter":3,"verse":18,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 4:28","book":"Act","chapter":4,"verse":28,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 5:30","book":"Act","chapter":5,"verse":30,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 26:24","book":"Mat","chapter":26,"verse":24},{"label":"Lk 22:22","book":"Luk","chapter":22,"verse":22},{"label":"Lk 24:20","book":"Luk","chapter":24,"verse":20},{"label":"Ac 3:18","book":"Act","chapter":3,"verse":18},{"label":"Ac 4:28","book":"Act","chapter":4,"verse":28},{"label":"Ac 5:30","book":"Act","chapter":5,"verse":30}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss read you have taken"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"God raised him up, ending the pains of death, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 8:11","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":11,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 6:14","book":"1Co","chapter":6,"verse":14,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 4:14","book":"2Co","chapter":4,"verse":14,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 1:20","book":"Eph","chapter":1,"verse":20,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 2:12","book":"Col","chapter":2,"verse":12,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 1:10","book":"1Th","chapter":1,"verse":10,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 13:20","book":"Heb","chapter":13,"verse":20,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" because it was not possible for him to be held by death. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 8:11","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":11},{"label":"1Co 6:14","book":"1Co","chapter":6,"verse":14},{"label":"2Co 4:14","book":"2Co","chapter":4,"verse":14},{"label":"Eph 1:20","book":"Eph","chapter":1,"verse":20},{"label":"Col 2:12","book":"Col","chapter":2,"verse":12},{"label":"1Th 1:10","book":"1Th","chapter":1,"verse":10},{"label":"Heb 13:20","book":"Heb","chapter":13,"verse":20}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For David says of him:"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:26","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Therefore my heart is glad"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:27","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"because you will not abandon me in Hades"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:28","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You have revealed the paths of life to me;"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:29","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Brothers and sisters, I can confidently speak to you about the patriarch David: He is both dead and buried, and his tomb is with us to this day. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Kg 2:10","book":"1Ki","chapter":2,"verse":10,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Neh 3:16","book":"Neh","chapter":3,"verse":16,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 7:8–9","book":"Act","chapter":7,"verse":8,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 13:36","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":36,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Kg 2:10","book":"1Ki","chapter":2,"verse":10},{"label":"Neh 3:16","book":"Neh","chapter":3,"verse":16},{"label":"Ac 7:8–9","book":"Act","chapter":7,"verse":8},{"label":"Ac 13:36","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":36}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:30","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Since he was a prophet, he knew that God had sworn an oath to him to seat one of his descendants "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss add according to the flesh to raise up the Messiah"},{"kind":"text","text":" on his throne. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Sm 23:2","book":"2Sa","chapter":23,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 132:11","book":"Psa","chapter":132,"verse":11,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 22:43","book":"Mat","chapter":22,"verse":43,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 1:32","book":"Luk","chapter":1,"verse":32,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 1:8","book":"Act","chapter":1,"verse":8,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 11:32","book":"Heb","chapter":11,"verse":32,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Sm 23:2","book":"2Sa","chapter":23,"verse":2},{"label":"Ps 132:11","book":"Psa","chapter":132,"verse":11},{"label":"Mt 22:43","book":"Mat","chapter":22,"verse":43},{"label":"Lk 1:32","book":"Luk","chapter":1,"verse":32},{"label":"Ac 1:8","book":"Act","chapter":1,"verse":8},{"label":"Heb 11:32","book":"Heb","chapter":11,"verse":32}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss add according to the flesh to raise up the Messiah"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:31","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Seeing what was to come, he spoke concerning the resurrection of the Messiah: He"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Other mss read His soul"},{"kind":"text","text":" was not abandoned in Hades, and his flesh did not experience decay."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 16:10","book":"Psa","chapter":16,"verse":10,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 16:10","book":"Psa","chapter":16,"verse":10,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 2:27","book":"Act","chapter":2,"verse":27,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 16:10","book":"Psa","chapter":16,"verse":10},{"label":"Ps 16:10","book":"Psa","chapter":16,"verse":10},{"label":"Ac 2:27","book":"Act","chapter":2,"verse":27}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Other mss read His soul"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:32","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“God has raised "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 18:33","book":"Luk","chapter":18,"verse":33,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 2:24","book":"Act","chapter":2,"verse":24,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" this Jesus; we are all witnesses of this. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 18:33","book":"Luk","chapter":18,"verse":33},{"label":"Ac 2:24","book":"Act","chapter":2,"verse":24}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:33","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Therefore, since he has been exalted to the right hand of God "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 2:9","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 10:12","book":"Heb","chapter":10,"verse":12,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" and has received from the Father the promised Holy Spirit, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 7:39","book":"Jhn","chapter":7,"verse":39,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 14:26","book":"Jhn","chapter":14,"verse":26,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 16:7","book":"Jhn","chapter":16,"verse":7,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 16:13","book":"Jhn","chapter":16,"verse":13,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" he has poured out "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 2:17","book":"Act","chapter":2,"verse":17,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 10:45","book":"Act","chapter":10,"verse":45,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"text","text":" what you both see and hear. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Php 2:9","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":9},{"label":"Heb 10:12","book":"Heb","chapter":10,"verse":12},{"label":"Jn 7:39","book":"Jhn","chapter":7,"verse":39},{"label":"Jn 14:26","book":"Jhn","chapter":14,"verse":26},{"label":"Jn 16:7","book":"Jhn","chapter":16,"verse":7},{"label":"Jn 16:13","book":"Jhn","chapter":16,"verse":13},{"label":"Ac 2:17","book":"Act","chapter":2,"verse":17},{"label":"Ac 10:45","book":"Act","chapter":10,"verse":45}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:34","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For it was not David who ascended into the heavens, but he himself says:"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:35","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"until I make your enemies your footstool.’"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 110:1","book":"Psa","chapter":110,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 110:1","book":"Psa","chapter":110,"verse":1,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 5:35","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":35,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 22:44","book":"Mat","chapter":22,"verse":44,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 12:36","book":"Mrk","chapter":12,"verse":36,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 20:42–43","book":"Luk","chapter":20,"verse":42,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 3:13","book":"Jhn","chapter":3,"verse":13,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 15:25","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":25,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 1:13","book":"Heb","chapter":1,"verse":13,"letter":"i"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 110:1","book":"Psa","chapter":110,"verse":1},{"label":"Ps 110:1","book":"Psa","chapter":110,"verse":1},{"label":"Mt 5:35","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":35},{"label":"Mt 22:44","book":"Mat","chapter":22,"verse":44},{"label":"Mk 12:36","book":"Mrk","chapter":12,"verse":36},{"label":"Lk 20:42–43","book":"Luk","chapter":20,"verse":42},{"label":"Jn 3:13","book":"Jhn","chapter":3,"verse":13},{"label":"1Co 15:25","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":25},{"label":"Heb 1:13","book":"Heb","chapter":1,"verse":13}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:36","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Therefore let all the house of Israel know with certainty that God has made this Jesus, whom you crucified, both Lord and Messiah.” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 28:18","book":"Mat","chapter":28,"verse":18,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 2:11","book":"Luk","chapter":2,"verse":11,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 14:9","book":"Rom","chapter":14,"verse":9,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 4:5","book":"2Co","chapter":4,"verse":5,"letter":"d"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 28:18","book":"Mat","chapter":28,"verse":18},{"label":"Lk 2:11","book":"Luk","chapter":2,"verse":11},{"label":"Rm 14:9","book":"Rom","chapter":14,"verse":9},{"label":"2Co 4:5","book":"2Co","chapter":4,"verse":5}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:37","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"When they heard this, they were pierced to the heart and said to Peter and the rest of the apostles, “Brothers, what should we do?” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 3:10","book":"Luk","chapter":3,"verse":10,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 16:30","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":30,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 3:10","book":"Luk","chapter":3,"verse":10},{"label":"Ac 16:30","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":30}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:38","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Peter replied, “Repent "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 24:47","book":"Luk","chapter":24,"verse":47,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 3:19","book":"Act","chapter":3,"verse":19,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 26:20","book":"Act","chapter":26,"verse":20,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" and be baptized, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 8:12","book":"Act","chapter":8,"verse":12,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 22:16","book":"Act","chapter":22,"verse":16,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" each of you, in the name "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 3:16","book":"Act","chapter":3,"verse":16,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 15:14","book":"Act","chapter":15,"verse":14,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" of Jesus Christ for the forgiveness of your sins, and you will receive the gift of the Holy Spirit. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 24:47","book":"Luk","chapter":24,"verse":47},{"label":"Ac 3:19","book":"Act","chapter":3,"verse":19},{"label":"Ac 26:20","book":"Act","chapter":26,"verse":20},{"label":"Ac 8:12","book":"Act","chapter":8,"verse":12},{"label":"Ac 22:16","book":"Act","chapter":22,"verse":16},{"label":"Ac 3:16","book":"Act","chapter":3,"verse":16},{"label":"Ac 15:14","book":"Act","chapter":15,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:39","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For the promise is for you and for your children, and for all who are far off, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 44:3","book":"Isa","chapter":44,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 3:25","book":"Act","chapter":3,"verse":25,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 2:13","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":13,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" as many as the Lord our God will call.” "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 44:3","book":"Isa","chapter":44,"verse":3},{"label":"Ac 3:25","book":"Act","chapter":3,"verse":25},{"label":"Eph 2:13","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":13}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:40","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"With many other words he testified and strongly urged them, saying, “Be saved from this corrupt "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or crooked, or twisted"},{"kind":"text","text":" generation!” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 32:5","book":"Deu","chapter":32,"verse":5,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 17:17","book":"Mat","chapter":17,"verse":17,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 2:15","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":15,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dt 32:5","book":"Deu","chapter":32,"verse":5},{"label":"Mt 17:17","book":"Mat","chapter":17,"verse":17},{"label":"Php 2:15","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":15}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or crooked, or twisted"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:41","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So those who accepted his message were baptized, and that day about three thousand people were added to them."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:42","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"They devoted themselves to the apostles’ teaching, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 5:28","book":"Act","chapter":5,"verse":28,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 13:12","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":12,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 17:19","book":"Act","chapter":17,"verse":19,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 14:6","book":"1Co","chapter":14,"verse":6,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" to the fellowship, to the breaking of bread, and to prayer. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 1:14","book":"Act","chapter":1,"verse":14,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 10:25","book":"Heb","chapter":10,"verse":25,"letter":"f"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 5:28","book":"Act","chapter":5,"verse":28},{"label":"Ac 13:12","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":12},{"label":"Ac 17:19","book":"Act","chapter":17,"verse":19},{"label":"1Co 14:6","book":"1Co","chapter":14,"verse":6},{"label":"Ac 1:14","book":"Act","chapter":1,"verse":14},{"label":"Heb 10:25","book":"Heb","chapter":10,"verse":25}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:43","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Everyone was filled with awe, and many wonders and signs were being performed through the apostles. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 16:17","book":"Mrk","chapter":16,"verse":17,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 16:20","book":"Mrk","chapter":16,"verse":20,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 5:12","book":"Act","chapter":5,"verse":12,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mk 16:17","book":"Mrk","chapter":16,"verse":17},{"label":"Mk 16:20","book":"Mrk","chapter":16,"verse":20},{"label":"Ac 5:12","book":"Act","chapter":5,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:44","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Now all the believers were together and held all things in common. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 19:21","book":"Mat","chapter":19,"verse":21,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 4:32","book":"Act","chapter":4,"verse":32,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 19:21","book":"Mat","chapter":19,"verse":21},{"label":"Ac 4:32","book":"Act","chapter":4,"verse":32}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:45","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"They sold their possessions and property and distributed the proceeds to all, as any had need. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:46","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Every day they devoted themselves to meeting together in the temple, and broke bread from house to house. They ate their food with joyful and sincere hearts, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 24:53","book":"Luk","chapter":24,"verse":53,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 5:42","book":"Act","chapter":5,"verse":42,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 20:7","book":"Act","chapter":20,"verse":7,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 24:53","book":"Luk","chapter":24,"verse":53},{"label":"Ac 5:42","book":"Act","chapter":5,"verse":42},{"label":"Ac 20:7","book":"Act","chapter":20,"verse":7}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:2:47","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"praising God and enjoying the favor of all the people. Every day the Lord added to their number "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss read to the church"},{"kind":"text","text":" those who were being saved. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 5:14","book":"Act","chapter":5,"verse":14,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 11:24","book":"Act","chapter":11,"verse":24,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 16:5","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":5,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 14:18","book":"Rom","chapter":14,"verse":18,"letter":"d"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 5:14","book":"Act","chapter":5,"verse":14},{"label":"Ac 11:24","book":"Act","chapter":11,"verse":24},{"label":"Ac 16:5","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":5},{"label":"Rm 14:18","book":"Rom","chapter":14,"verse":18}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss read to the church"}]}]},"cachedAt":1783099522951}